FBIS4-12546 "drnes069_v_94008" FBIS-NES-94-069 Daily Report 11 Apr 1994 Pakistan UN Emissary, President Discuss Finding Afghan Solution UN Emissary, President Discuss Finding Afghan Solution NC1104063094 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran First Program Network in Persian 0330 GMT 11 Apr 94 NC1104063094 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran First Program Network Persian BFN [Text] Mahmud Mestiri, the head of the special UN delegation to Afghanistan, met Pakistani President Farooq Leghari yesterday. According to the Central News Unit, the meeting in Islamabad discussed ways and means to reach an amicable solution to end the civil war in Afghanistan.
